people  are  using  back  and  forth  to  construction  sites,  or  wherever 
they  need  them  for  work,  but  the  larger  vehicles  that  people  are 
using  to  essentially  drive  around  town.  They’re  using  them  mostly 
as a passenger vehicle, and we’ve included those. So, it’s essentially 
super  large  pickup  trucks  that  were  not  included.  Everything  else 
is included. 

