a whole bunch of things. It would change the entire demand curve 
of our country. 

I’m  not  saying  any  one  of  those  is  the  best  thing  to  do,  or  100 
percent  correct,  but  I  know  this,  we’re  not  doing  any  of  it.  We  are 
