us  jobs,  and  it’s  costing  us  health  costs  and—asthma  and  other 
things  from  the  air  quality.  You  name  it.  We’re  not  even  meeting 
those standards. 

So,  I  hope  you  all  will,  you  know,  do  something.  But,  in  the 

meantime, I hope we will, Mr. Chairman. Thanks. 

